title: How to Reset for a New Month!
itunes:title: How to Reset for a New Month!
description:
In this episode, Kimberly Cobb updates us on her Urgent Care visit and getting harassed by a creep, announces her vlogging series, shares her tips on how to reset at the start of a new month, and more!

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life! Thanks for listening!
